= Introduction =

This is a showcase of Web-2.0 applications that have been
access-enabled using AxsJAX. [http://google-axsjax.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/docs/faq.html For more details, please read the AxsJAX FAQ.]

  * [http://www.google.com Google Web Search] [http://google-axsjax.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/docs/search_userguide.html User Guide]

  * [http://mail.google.com Google Gmail] [http://google-axsjax.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/docs/gmail_userguide.html User Guide]

  * [http://calendar.google.com Google Calendar] [http://google-axsjax.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/docs/calendar_userguide.html User Guide]

  * [http://reader.google.com Google Reader] [http://google-axsjax.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/docs/reader_userguide.html User Guide]

  * [http://scholar.google.com Google Scholar]  [http://google-axsjax.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/docs/scholar_userguide.html User Guide]

  * [http://books.google.com Google Books]  [http://google-axsjax.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/docs/books_userguide.html User Guide]

  * [http://www.minijuegosgratis.com/juegos/jawbreaker/jawbreaker.htm Jawbreaker Game] [http://google-axsjax.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/docs/jawbreaker_userguide.html User Guide]

  * [http://xkcd.com/ The xkcd Web Comic] [http://google-axsjax.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/docs/xkcd_userguide.html User Guide]
